dct_description_sm: Dot distribution map. Includes ancillary computer generated isopleth map Cattle and calves: number per 1,000 acres of cropland, 1964. ASCII-art map created using SYMAP or similar technique.    Detached from: An atlas of Indiana / by Robert C. Kingsbury , with contributions from John M. Hollingsworth and others. Bloomington, Indiana : Department of Geography, Indiana University, [1970]. Page 71.
Imprint: Bloomington, Indiana : Department of Geography, Indiana University, [1970]
